object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM operations.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code ='ACX'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM operations.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code ='ACX'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT
    -- Keys
    CAST(TRIM(bronze_aeas.system_id) AS INT) AS source_system_system_id,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.parent_id) AS source_system_parent_id,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.cmm_container) AS predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_type,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.id) AS predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_source_system_key,

    -- Direct mappings
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.originating_source_name) AS originating_source_name,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.originating_load_type) AS originating_load_type,
    cb.batch_id AS predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_batch_id,

    TRIM(bronze_aeas.assessment_id) AS assessment_id,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.solution_id) AS solution_id,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.solution_name) AS solution_name,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.business_function) AS business_function,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.assessed_entity) AS assessed_entity,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.category) AS assessment_category,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.score) AS assessment_score,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.score_percentile) AS assessment_score_percentile,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.normalized_score) AS assessment_normalized_score,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.recommended_action_description) AS assessment_recommended_action_description,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.recommended_action_code) AS assessment_recommended_action_code,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.conclusion_description) AS assessment_conclusion_description,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.conclusion_code) AS assessment_conclusion_code,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.score_date) AS assessment_score_date,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.assesment_detail) AS assesment_detail,
    TRIM(bronze_aeas.error) AS assessment_error,
    CAST(TRIM(bronze_aeas.row_id) AS BIGINT) AS source_system_row_id,

    -- Existing row for update logic
    silver_paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_md5checksum
FROM bronze.acx_ea_assessment_summary bronze_aeas
LEFT JOIN silver.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary silver_paas
    ON CAST(TRIM(bronze_aeas.system_id) AS INT) = CAST(silver_paas.source_system_system_id AS INT)
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(bronze_aeas.parent_id), '') = COALESCE(silver_paas.source_system_parent_id, '')
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(bronze_aeas.cmm_container), '') = COALESCE(silver_paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_type, '')
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(bronze_aeas.id), '') = COALESCE(silver_paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_source_system_key, '')
   AND silver_paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
   AND silver_paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_status = 'Active'
CROSS JOIN current_batch cb
ORDER BY 
    bronze_aeas.system_id,
    bronze_aeas.parent_id,
    bronze_aeas.cmm_container,
    bronze_aeas.id;
